But she'll be so far away. I don't know what I'm gonna do without my Monkey.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NYRaHvw</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[hahway]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Importance of a good ball boy</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uM7SBWM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5Zs8NsU.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uM7SBWM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HotCoffee9520]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hello from Ireland</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZrDsfAs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NiqsBzg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ZrDsfAs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[spookkoops]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Family first</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QS8SPWR</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VwfzNmn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/QS8SPWR</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vtrvcr]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I’ve made my choice</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9qU5LJh</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rLcH50P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9qU5LJh</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LimJahey504]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>M.I.B.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JINcgpW</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BVkIXxK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>One of the best scenes</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JINcgpW</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DarthCynical]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sugar pulling machine</title